title: 108 CND - VINYLUX CREAM PUFF Weekly Polish Bright White Nail Coat Manicure 0.5oz
description:
What Is It

From the makers of CND Shellac (The Original Power Polish!) comes VINYLUX Weekly Polish, the new breakthrough nail polish that provides 7+ days of high gloss, chip-free wear, without the use of a base coat!

How It Works

The innovative self-adhering color coat system, eliminates the need for a base coat and dries in under nine minutes, saving you time and hassle. While other polishes deteriorate on your nails over time, VINYLUX endures and strengthens in resistance. The ProLight technology of the VINYLUX Top Coat creates a network of cross-linked polymer bonds that build resistance when exposed to natural light, effortlessly securing shine and resistance while you go about your day!
